description:
Awesome 1 bedroom with office. Quiet, views of huron street and backyard. Half of second floor of charming building. Bohemian vibe, clean, and chill. Great sunlight. 

My place is close to Anella, Achilles Heel, Alameda, Propeller Coffee, and Troost. You’ll love my place because of the ambiance, the neighborhood, and the light.
name: Spacious Greenpoint 1 Bedroom 1 Bathroom :)
review: Great place and host! Recommend it!
